<p align="center"><b>Build artifacts just like grandma used to make.</b></p>

<p align="center">
  <a href="https://github.com/LioraLabs/cook/actions/workflows/ci.yml"><img src="https://github.com/LioraLabs/cook/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg" alt="CI"></a>
